There is only one train in Toyland landscape:
*[[File:en/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Wizzowowrocketeer.png|Wizzowow Rocketeer]] [[en/Manual/Base Set/Trains/Wizzowow Rocketeer]]

None of the MagLev vehicles in OpenTTD have a real-life relative; they are purely fictional.

